**bitcoinlocator** was a location service that showed the locations on a map where goods and services of the Bitcoin economy were offered. The service allowed service providers, exchanges and merchants to participate by adding a marker to the map so that the visitor to the site only sees nearby offers.

##History
This service was first offered on July 20, 2011. (2.1) The site has since closed.[[!template id=when]]

